---
import SiteLayout from '../../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout title="Contribute" description="Submit AI paper review prompts to ReviewPrompt." locale="en">
  <section class="aw-page-hero">
    <div class="aw-container">
      <p class="aw-eyebrow">Contribute</p>
      <h1>Contribute</h1>
      <p>ReviewPrompt currently accepts AI paper review prompt submissions only.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="aw-container aw-section compact">
    <div class="aw-content-card">
      <h2>What to Submit</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Whether it supports full paper review or rebuttal.</li>
        <li>Whether it is designed for authors or reviewers.</li>
        <li>The expected input and output.</li>
        <li>Known limitations and safety concerns.</li>
        <li>License, source, and contributor attribution.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Submission Path</h2>
      <p>Use the GitHub Issue Form to submit a prompt.</p>

      <h2>Review Criteria</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Clear task and target user.</li>
        <li>Evidence-aware output format.</li>
        <li>No fabricated citations or venue policies.</li>
        <li>Usable examples or templates.</li>
        <li>Compatible license.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
